This pattern will take advantage of Delta Lake's guarantee that the latest version of the static Delta table is returned each time it is queried.
in stream staic join, the streaming portion of the join drives the join process.Only new data appearing on the streaming side of the join will trigger the processing.While adding new records into the static table, will not automatically trigger updates to the results.Even though the new records in static table it does not effect and missed from the resulting table when not present during the streaming.
